          "title": "Definitions",
          "html": "<p><strong>1.1.3.2. Definitions</strong></p><p>In this Code,</p><p><em>Alternative measure</em> means a substitute for a provision of this Code that will achieve the level of performance required by the applicable objectives and functional statements.</p><p><em>Private sewage disposal system</em> means a sewage system that serves only one lot.</p><p><em>Sewage system</em> means a works for the collection, transmission, treatment and disposal of sewage.</p>",
