          "effective_date": "1998-04-06",
          "ineffective_date": null,
          "title": "Fire Separations",
          "html": "<p><strong>3.1.4.7. Fire Separations</strong></p><p>(1) Except as provided in Sentences (2) to (7) and Articles 3.1.4.8. to 3.1.4.11., every <em>fire separation</em> shall have a <em>fire-resistance rating</em> not less than that shown in Table 3.1.4.7.</p><p>(2) A fire separation between a <em>suite</em> and an adjacent corridor serving that suite shall have a fire-resistance rating not less than that required for a <em>floor assembly</em>.</p><p>(3) A fire separation between a <em>service room</em> and the remainder of the <em>building</em> shall have a fire-resistance rating not less than 1 h.</p>",
          "page_images": [],
