          "effective_date": "1998-04-06",
          "ineffective_date": null,
          "title": "",
          "html": "<p>The definitions provided in Article 1.1.3.2. are essential for the correct interpretation of the Code. Many terms have meanings that differ from everyday usage. For example, <em>alternative measure</em> has a precise legal meaning within the Code framework that permits performance-based solutions as substitutes for prescriptive requirements.</p>",
